---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { author } from "../data/socials";
---

<Layout title={`Experience - ${author}`}>
  <div class="space-y-16">
    <!-- Page Header -->
    <section class="space-y-4">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-foreground">
        Professional Journey
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground">
        Over 8 years of building scalable data solutions and driving technical innovation
        across startups and enterprises.
      </p>
      <p class="text-base text-muted-foreground">
        From customer service to founding a data analytics company to leading engineering
        at AI startups—each role taught me something new about turning data challenges
        into automated solutions.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- Job Entries -->
    <section class="space-y-12">

      <!-- Forage AI -->
      <article class="space-y-4 p-6 bg-card rounded-lg border-l-4 border-primary">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-foreground">
            Forage AI
          </h2>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary">
            Senior Data Engineer
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground italic">
            January 2024 - Present • Chennai, India
          </p>
        </div>

        <p class="text-card-foreground">
          Leading development of automated data collection and processing systems for an
          AI-powered data extraction platform.
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-3">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-foreground">Impact:</h4>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-card-foreground">
            <li>Architected public social media web scraping frameworks processing 1M+ records daily</li>
            <li>Achieved 99.5% uptime through robust error handling and monitoring</li>
            <li>Reduced data processing time by 70% through automation</li>
            <li>Integrated LLMs for intelligent extraction from complex documents</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-3">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-foreground">What I Built:</h4>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-card-foreground">
            <li>Production-grade Scrapy frameworks handling 100+ concurrent data sources</li>
            <li>NLP pipelines for parsing and structuring unstructured content</li>
            <li>Automated workflows eliminating manual data processing tasks</li>
            <li>Real-time monitoring dashboards for system health</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-2">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-foreground">Technical Environment:</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">
            Python, Scrapy, Playwright, OpenAI API, NLP, AWS (ECS, S3, Lambda), PostgreSQL,
            Docker, Redis, Celery
          </p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- TCS -->
      <article class="space-y-4 p-6 bg-card rounded-lg border-l-4 border-primary">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-foreground">
            Tata Consultancy Services
          </h2>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary">
            Performance Engineer (Client: SKY)
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground italic">
            January 2022 - January 2023 • Chennai, India
          </p>
        </div>

        <p class="text-card-foreground">
          Led performance monitoring and optimization for containerized microservices
          serving millions of users.
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-3">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-foreground">Key Achievements:</h4>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-card-foreground">
            <li>Reduced incident response time by 60% through automated monitoring</li>
            <li>Implemented comprehensive performance testing framework</li>
            <li>Managed 50+ containerized applications in CI/CD pipelines</li>
            <li>Created Grafana dashboards for real-time performance insights</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-3">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-foreground">Responsibilities:</h4>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-card-foreground">
            <li>Developed and maintained API endpoint performance monitoring systems</li>
            <li>Implemented Prometheus/Grafana monitoring stack</li>
            <li>Troubleshot production issues through log analysis and container inspection</li>
            <li>Collaborated with engineering teams on performance optimization</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-2">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-foreground">Technical Environment:</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">
            Prometheus, Grafana, Docker, Kubernetes, Python, Jenkins, Linux, Git
          </p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- Lapis Data Analytics -->
      <article class="space-y-4 p-6 bg-card rounded-lg border-l-4 border-primary">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-foreground">
            Lapis Data Analytics
          </h2>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary">
            Co-Founder | Lead Python Developer | Data Engineer
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground italic">
            January 2021 - January 2022 • Chennai, India
          </p>
        </div>

        <p class="text-card-foreground">
          Founded and led technical operations for a data analytics consultancy serving
          B2B clients.
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-3">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-foreground">Entrepreneurial Journey:</h4>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-card-foreground">
            <li>Built company from ground up, establishing technical infrastructure</li>
            <li>Led Python development projects for multiple clients simultaneously</li>
            <li>Managed all technical operations: security, infrastructure, networks</li>
            <li>Evaluated and adopted emerging technologies for competitive advantage</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-3">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-foreground">Business Impact:</h4>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-card-foreground">
            <li>Delivered custom data solutions to diverse client portfolio</li>
            <li>Built reputation for reliable, high-quality technical delivery</li>
            <li>Established processes for scalable project management</li>
            <li>Created reusable frameworks reducing project delivery time</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-2">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-foreground">Technical Focus:</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">
            Python, Django, Flask, PostgreSQL, AWS, Linux, Project Management, Client Relations
          </p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- Zudo Innovations (Edvoy) -->
      <article class="space-y-4 p-6 bg-card rounded-lg border-l-4 border-primary">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-foreground">
            Zudo Innovations (Edvoy)
          </h2>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary">
            Senior Data Analyst | Python Developer
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground italic">
            December 2019 - December 2020 • Chennai, India
          </p>
        </div>

        <p class="text-card-foreground">
          Led development of large-scale data collection systems for education technology
          platform connecting students with universities worldwide.
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-3">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-foreground">Major Projects:</h4>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-card-foreground">
            <li>Built Scrapy framework collecting course/scholarship data from 200+ websites</li>
            <li>Architected NoSQL backend handling millions of education records</li>
            <li>Developed web dashboards enabling data audit team efficiency</li>
            <li>Implemented browser automation for dynamic content extraction</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-3">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-foreground">Innovation:</h4>
          <p class="text-card-foreground">
            Pioneered browser rendering approach that abstracted away website complexity,
            allowing developers to program based on visible data rather than underlying HTML.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-3">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-foreground">Leadership:</h4>
          <p class="text-card-foreground">
            Managed team of developers, coordinated sprints, ensured quality delivery
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-2">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-foreground">Technical Stack:</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">
            Scrapy, Selenium, MongoDB, Python, Django, AWS, Docker, Redis, Celery
          </p>
        </div>
      </article>

    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
